CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg. 14 reads: "Index Department-Front to rear: Cecelia E. Sandok, special index clerk; Catherine Stuba, typist. Standing: Sarah Hardy, special index clerk, and Gertrude Gorzoch, typist."
TitMainTitle: Interior of Index Department of Allegheny County Prothonotary office, with man and women working at desks including Cecelia E. Sandok, Catherine Stuba, Sarah Harde, and Gertrude Gorzpch, Russell Index Company calendar and map of Allegheny County on wall
